<ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;"><li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">(delight): High contentment, satisfaction, and inner happiness.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Our happiness should be derived from getting more insight into the character of God through His laws.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Truly happy people will seek their direction for life from God.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">&quot;Live by your truth and you can be whatever you want to be.&quot; is one of the largest lies to oneself that people make in modern culture. This ideology and aim will never lead to fulfillment because humans can never aspire to fulfill their own desires. More selfish desire will always be waiting at the end of the road onto the next.</li>
<li style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Psalm 14:1: Only the fool says in his heart, there is no God. Rejection of God leads to severe unhappiness, unfulfillment, and even punishment.</li></ul></body></html>